Subject: [PATCH] 8993: Annotations: Location context and Variable handler

Annotations: Variable handler

Two possible forms are supported:
	{@var <var_sym> [<func_sym>]}
and
	{@var_hash <var_hash> <func_sym>}

Update the modify function in the AnnotatedStringHandler interface to support comment location. Update corresponding handlers and tests.

Add documentation for Variable Annotation. Remove incorrect note for Symbol Annotation.
